{"tid":1854422,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"巴基斯坦宣佈禁止中國航班入境 政府拒絕交代原因","createTime":"2020-01-31T13:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T17:37:59.000Z","uid":133680,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"9890d0e6302af2ec331d1231b0335c00aac4e0ec","tid":1854422,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2553119/%E9%90%B5%E6%A1%BF%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F%E4%B9%9F%E8%A6%81%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%20%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%BE%86%E5%BE%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%20%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2553119%2F%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%25A1%25BF%25E5%2585%2584%25E5%25BC%259F%25E4%25B9%259F%25E8%25A6%2581%25E9%2598%25B2%25E7%2596%25AB%2520%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%259D%25A6%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E4%25BE%2586%25E5%25BE%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%258F%25AD%2520%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=7d608bdb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2553119/%E9%90%B5%E6%A1%BF%E5%85%84%E5%BC%9F%E4%B9%9F%E8%A6%81%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB%20%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E5%9D%A6%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%BE%86%E5%BE%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%20%E9%98%B2%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E</a><br />\n鐵桿兄弟也要防疫 巴基斯坦暫停來往中國航班 防武漢肺炎<br />\n鐵桿兄弟也要防疫 巴基斯坦暫停來往中國航班 防武漢肺炎<br />\n 環球社會熱點 14:32 2020/01/31 <br />\n新型冠狀病毒武漢肺炎疫情蔓延，中國「鐵桿兄弟」巴基斯坦也採取防範措施，暫停來往中國航班<br />\n<br />\n▲ 新型冠狀病毒武漢肺炎疫情蔓延，中國「鐵桿兄弟」巴基斯坦也採取防範措施，暫停來往中國航班<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新型冠狀病毒疫情繼續擴散，武漢肺炎確診個案持續上升，中國「鐵桿兄弟」巴基斯坦也採取防範措施。巴基斯坦民航局宣布，即日起停止往返中國內地航線，直到2月2日。防止武漢肺炎擴散，全球多間航空公司亦已經採取相同做法，包括英國航空（ British Airways）、南韓首爾航空（Air Seoul）及印尼獅子航空（Lion Air）。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦民航局部長科克哈爾（Abdul Sattar Khokhar）受路透社訪問稱：「我們將暫停飛往中國的航班，直到2月2日。」<br />\n<br />\n日本周六起列為指定感染症 拒武漢肺炎患者入境<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加拿大恐慌新型冠狀病毒 現排華情緒 <br />\n<br />\n他補充，在此日期之後將對局勢進行審查。不過他拒絕評論停飛原因。<br />\n<br />\n早前，英國航空宣佈，暫停所有前往中國北京及上海航班，直至至少3月。英航來往香港航班暫時不受影響。"},{"pid":"5fd6873e60836c025c7758b1be68b6dc8bbf0f06","tid":1854422,"uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:03:17.000Z","msg":"巴鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bddd82d33a34438e733efa2608220513ec9be07","tid":1854422,"uid":84102,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:03:39.000Z","msg":"心照啦 交代條撚咩"},{"pid":"3884e5a715882e841f5a8392eacfbbcdfe430212","tid":1854422,"uid":304512,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"所謂巴鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03e06b3ff1856e60d71cf214070cf618151869e","tid":1854422,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b37fbb635e6c5e10edebce1a15c173dfe094375","tid":1854422,"uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"衰撚過巴基斯坦<br />\n最撚慘既係連埋香港一齊封<br />\n香港人要留係香港等死"},{"pid":"8abf6774c3d01e476378902c4835b6af0380cdd3","tid":1854422,"uid":290118,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"甴種個一帶一路仲點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ffca056cb603a57e0f044998d9a35dd1755996","tid":1854422,"uid":3080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T13:08:42.000Z","msg":"停得嗰幾日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\